{"id":390,"date":"2020-10-12T16:33:36","date_gmt":"2020-10-12T14:33:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/xanasoft.com\/?page_id=390"},"modified":"2023-04-29T07:38:39","modified_gmt":"2023-04-29T07:38:39","slug":"lingerprocess","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/sandboxie\/lingerprocess\/","title":{"rendered":"Linger Process"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1>Linger Process<\/h1>\n<p><em>LingerProcess<\/em> is a sandbox setting in <a href=\"SandboxieIni\">Sandboxie Ini<\/a>. It specifies names of programs that will be automatically terminated, when they are the last programs that remain in execution in a particular sandbox. This is useful as some programs occasionally launch <em>helper programs<\/em> to carry out a specific task, and the helper program remains in execution even after the original program has ended. For example:<\/p>\n<pre><code>   .\n   .\n   .\n   [DefaultBox]\n   LingerProcess=jusched.exe<\/code><\/pre>\n<p><em>jusched.exe<\/em> is part of the Sun Java framework. It is occasionally launched when Internet Explorer starts the Java framework. This <em>LingerProcess<\/em> example setting specifies that if <em>jusched.exe<\/em> remains the last program running in the sandbox DefaultBox, then it should be terminated.<\/p>\n<p>LingerProcess will not terminate a process, if that process was the first process launched in the sandbox.<\/p>\n<p>For example, the default configuration includes Adobe Acrobat Reader as a LingerProcess, because it is typically launched when viewing PDF files through the Web browser, and remains running even after the browser has closed.<\/p>\n<pre><code>   LingerProcess=acrord32.exe<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>However, if you manually start Adobe Acrobat Reader sandboxed, for example by running it from the Sandboxie Start Menu, then the LingerProcess setting will not apply to that process.<\/p>\n<p>Related <a href=\"SandboxieControl\">Sandboxie Control<\/a> setting: <a href=\"ProgramStopSettings#lingering-programs\">Sandbox Settings -&gt; Program Stop -&gt; Lingering Programs<\/a><\/p>\n<p>See also: <a href=\"ProgramSettings#linger\">Program Settings<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Linger Process LingerProcess is a sandbox setting in Sandboxie Ini. It specifies names of programs that will be automatically terminated, when they are the last programs that remain in execution in a particular sandbox. This is useful as some programs occasionally launch helper programs to carry out a specific task, and the helper program remains &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/sandboxie\/lingerprocess\/\" class=\"more-link\">Continue reading <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Linger Process<\/span> <span class=\"meta-nav\">&rarr;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":108,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/390"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=390"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/390\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2148,"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/390\/revisions\/2148"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/108"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sandboxie-plus.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=390"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}